---

---

<section
    id="contacto"
    class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-purple-700 relative overflow-hidden"
>
    <!-- Background patterns -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 background-pattern">
        <svg
            class="w-full h-full"
            width="100%"
            height="100%"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
            <defs>
                <pattern
                    id="grid"
                    width="40"
                    height="40"
                    patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
                >
                    <path
                        d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="white"
                        stroke-width="1"></path>
                </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid)"></rect>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
        <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight"
        >
            ¿Listo para dejar de buscar y <br /> empezar a encontrar?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Da el primer paso hoy. Envíanos un mensaje directo en Instagram para
            reservar tu diagnóstico gratuito o solicitar más información.
        </p>

        <div
            class="bg-white p-2 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl inline-block max-w-full w-full md:w-auto hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
            <!-- Instagram Interaction -->
            <div
                class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-between p-6 md:p-8"
            >
                <div class="text-left">
                    <p
                        class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                    >
                        Hablemos ahora
                    </p>
                    <p
                        class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-8 h-8 text-pink-600"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            aria-hidden="true"
                            ><path
                                fill-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M12.315 2c2.43 0 2.784.013 3.808.06 1.064.049 1.791.218 2.427.465a4.902 4.902 0 011.772 1.153 4.902 4.902 0 011.153 1.772c.247.636.416 1.363.465 2.427.048 1.067.06 1.407.06 4.123v.08c0 2.643-.012 2.987-.06 4.043-.049 1.064-.218 1.791-.465 2.427a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153 1.772 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772 1.153c-.636.247-1.363.416-2.427.465-1.067.048-1.407.06-4.123.06h-.08c-2.643 0-2.987-.012-4.043-.06-1.064-.049-1.791-.218-2.427-.465a4.902 4.902 0 01-1.772-1.153 4.902 4.902 0 01-1.153-1.772c-.247-.636-.416-1.363-.465-2.427-.047-1.024-.06-1.379-.06-3.808v-.63c0-2.43.013-2.784.06-3.808.049-1.064.218-1.791.465-2.427a4.902 4.902 0 011.153-1.772 4.902 4.902 0 011.772-1.153c.636-.247 1.363-.416 2.427-.465 1.067-.047 1.409-.06 3.809-.06a4.424 4.424 0 012.095.068zm2.093 11.949a2.956 2.956 0 10-2.093 2.093l2.093-2.093zm-5.63-2.093a2.956 2.956 0 102.093-2.093l-2.093 2.093zm7.04-5.46a.965.965 0 11-.965.965.965.965 0 01.965-.965z"
                                clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
                        >
                        Envíanos un DM
                    </p>
                </div>
                <a
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/somosempleables/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="group w-full md:w-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-pink-500/30 transition-all text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
                >
                    <span>Contactar por Instagram</span>
                    <svg
                        class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        ><path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg
                    >
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-blue-200 opacity-80">
            * Menciona "Informes" en tu mensaje para atención prioritaria.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
